---
description: Data access and normalization rules
alwaysApply: true
---

Use validated official Montgomery data whenever possible.

Rules:
- Normalize external payloads in service files
- UI components must not consume raw ArcGIS payloads directly
- Handle loading, empty, and error states explicitly
- Prefer graceful degradation over brittle assumptions
- Keep the MVP read-only
- If a field or endpoint is uncertain, surface that uncertainty clearly

Do not fabricate data behavior.
Do not assume undocumented fields exist.
